Bobabili basungule iMove The Nation, sebegijime izinsuku eziwu-16. Ngosuku bebegijima * -35km kanti namhlanje kulindeleke ukuthi bagijime besuka eMgungundlovu balibangise eThekwini kuhle kweComrades Marathon. Bobabili sebake bayigijima izikhawu iComrades Marathon. Ngesikhathi beqala babenehloso yokuqoqa uR6 million ozokondla izingane eziwu-10 000 ezweni. Ezinsukwini ezedlule asebegijime kuzo amakhilomitha awu-500 sebeqoqe imali engaphezu kukaR1 268 034. Phakathi kwababesekayo kubalwa kubo iShoprite, Hollywood Bets, C16 Running Crew, Little Ashford, Areshumeng Holdings neFerguson Films. I-Old Mutual inikele ngoR1.1 million. Ukugijima bazokugoqa eSouth Beach. Ofuna ukunikela ungena ku-www.hopewitheverystep.com.